fields.question: What is Tutor Sphere?
fields.answer: Tutor Sphere is an online tutor app designed to connect students with experienced tutors for personalized learning experiences. It provides a platform where students can find tutors for various subjects, schedule sessions, and engage in real-time communication through messaging and video calls.

fields.question: Is there a way for students to reschedule or cancel sessions?
fields.answer: Yes, students can easily reschedule or cancel sessions through the app, depending on the tutorÆs availability and preferences.

fields.question: What types of subjects can be tutored on Tutor Sphere?
fields.answer: Tutor Sphere supports a wide range of subjects including mathematics, science, languages, arts, coding, test preparation, and more, catering to diverse academic needs.

fields.question: Can Tutor Sphere handle group sessions?
fields.answer: Currently, Tutor Sphere focuses on one-on-one tutoring, but future updates may include options for group sessions or workshops depending on user demand.

fields.question: Can students rate and review tutors on Tutor Sphere?
fields.answer: Yes, students can provide ratings and reviews for tutors after each session, helping other users make informed decisions when choosing a tutor based on their experience and feedback.
